## Security Risks Mitigated

The CI/CD pipeline integrates multiple security mechanisms to protect the software delivery process.

### Code Vulnerabilities
SonarQube scans application code to identify security vulnerabilities such as injection flaws, insecure dependencies, and poor coding practices.

### Container Vulnerabilities
Trivy scans container images for known vulnerabilities in operating system packages and third-party libraries.

### Unauthorized Infrastructure Changes
GitOps ensures that all infrastructure configurations are managed through Git repositories, preventing unauthorized manual modifications.

### Deployment Integrity
Argo CD continuously reconciles the Kubernetes cluster with the desired state defined in the Git repository, preventing configuration drift.

### Deployment Monitoring
Slack notifications provide visibility into pipeline execution and allow teams to respond quickly to failures.
